AGRICULTURE CODE

statute or by rule of the board. The department shall prescribe the
format of the label.
(d) The department shall fix and collect a fee for the issuance
of a certification label in an amount necessary to cover the costs of
inspection and labels.
Acts 1981, 67th Leg., p. 1137, ch. 388, Sec. 1, eff. Sept. 1, 1981.
Amended by Acts 2001, 77th Leg., ch. 52, Sec. 9, eff. May 7, 2001.

